snippet: Only children, with a sprinkling of adult supervision, will be permitted to attend the Jan. 19 Dutch Cup replay between Ajax and AZ.
abstract: Only children, with a sprinkling of adult supervision, will be permitted to attend the Jan. 19 Dutch Cup replay between Ajax and AZ.
lead_paragraph: The replay of the Dutch Cup match between Ajax and AZ, which was abandoned on Dec. 21 and is scheduled to be played on Jan. 19, will be for children only.

headline.main: In the Netherlands, a Child's Game for Children Only
